yze in this paper they seem to decay faster than\nthe quasi-bound states. Finally, we speculate about the possibility that these\nconfigurations could describe the innermost regions of dark matter halos.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Apr 2017 17:56:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-02"}
