ion, DQfD leverages human demonstrations to achieve\nstate-of-the-art results for 11 games. Finally, we show that DQfD performs\nbetter than three related algorithms for incorporating demonstration data into\nDQN.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Apr 2017 12:44:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Jul 2017 13:19:52 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 21 Jul 2017 10:48:28 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 22 Nov 2017 21:18:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-27"}
